'''Gilad''' was the first name of these individuals:

==Canon==
*'''[[Gilad Pellaeon]]''', an [[Galactic Empire|Imperial]] [[captain]] that served in the [[Third Fleet]] and [[7th Fleet|Seventh Fleet]].

==Legends==
*'''[[Gilad Pellaeon/Legends|Gilad Pellaeon]]''', the leader of the [[Imperial Remnant]].
*'''[[Gilad Halsek]]''', the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Consul-General]] of [[Kothlis]].

